      public Image(int mazeID, int positionX, int positionY, cellState state, int imageHeight, int imageWidth, String imageDescription)
      An image that can be inserted into a maze
      Parameters:
      mazeID - the identification of the maze the image is inserted into
      positionX - the horizontal position of the image in the maze
      positionY - the vertical position of the image in the maze
      state - the state of the cells the image is touching
      imageHeight - the height of the image
      imageWidth - the width of the image
      imageDescription - the description of the image
